WEBVTT

00:03:59.418 --> 00:04:00.418
(Laughter)

00:04:01.246 --> 00:04:03.305
But this time, I took it further.

00:04:04.150 --> 00:04:05.864
I started a band with my friends.

00:04:06.594 --> 00:04:08.714
We wrote songs and recorded them.

00:04:08.738 --> 00:04:12.014
We even played gigs to real people.

00:04:13.184 --> 00:04:14.350
Not as many as this.

00:04:14.374 --> 00:04:17.128
(Laughter)

00:04:17.152 --> 00:04:19.201
But even though it was a just a tiny step,

00:04:19.225 --> 00:04:23.312
it was a giant leap from what I'd achieved
when I was all in one piece.

00:04:26.362 --> 00:04:29.996
Now while relearning every action
that one has ever cultivated